Results of traffic counts on Queensway (A442) at Trench on Wed.May 22nd. from 13.15-13.30 and Fri.May 24th.from 10.00-10.15
{Southbound Northbound } Wed. Fri. Wed. Fri. {Cars 69 80 94 60 {Lorries 11 9 13 17 {Vans 15 9 18 9 {Bicycles 1 2 1 1 {Mo'bikes 3 0 3 0 {Tractor 1 0 1 0 {Bus 0 0 1 0}
The total number of vehicles using the southbound carriageway was the same on both Wednesday and Friday.The traffic on the northbound carriageway was much heavier on Wednesday.This may have been because the count was taken at lunchtime and people were going home.
